| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5399 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: f931dfbf-8f38-5ff9-9f8a-04360c0db924"
